      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Home className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Custom Real Estate Web Design</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Tailored websites for residential agents, commercial brokers, and luxury property specialists. Your brand, your market, your results.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-green-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Search className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">IDX/MLS Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Seamless property search functionality. Your listings update automatically—no manual work required.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M22 16.92V19a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.86 19.86 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.86 19.86 0 0 1 3 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 5 2h2.09a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.12.86.3 1.7.54 2.5a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.41a16 16 0 0 0 6.5 6.5l1.08-1.09a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.8.24 1.64.42 2.5.54A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Mobile-Responsive Design</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Over 75% of property searches happen on mobile. Your site looks perfect on every device.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-green-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Target className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Lead Capture Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Strategic contact forms, property alerts, and home valuation tools that convert browsers into qualified leads.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Pin className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Neighborhood & Market Pages</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">SEO-optimized pages for every area you serve—rank for "homes for sale in [your city]" and dominate local search.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-green-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Camera className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Virtual Tour Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Showcase properties with 3D tours, video walkthroughs, and photo galleries that sell homes faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Work With Me Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-green-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decoration -->
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-black">Why Real Estate Agents Choose Me</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-green-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">Industry expertise and proven results for real estate success</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-12 border border-green-100">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Real Estate Industry Expertise</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">I understand MLS systems, lead generation, and what converts property shoppers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Target className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Proven Lead Generation</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Every design element focuses on capturing and nurturing qualified leads.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
                <path d="M2 12h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                <path d="M12 2c3 3 4.5 6.5 4.5 10S15 19 12 22c-3-3-4.5-6.5-4.5-10S9 5 12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Local SEO Mastery</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Optimize for neighborhood searches and "realtor near me" queries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Zap className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Fast & Scalable</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Websites that handle high traffic during open houses and new listings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Clock className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Quick Launch</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Most real estate sites completed in 2-3 weeks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-green-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decoration -->
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-black">Every Real Estate Website I Build Includes:</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-12 border border-green-100">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Custom professional design</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Mobile-responsive layout</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">IDX/MLS property search</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Agent bio & credentials</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Featured listings showcase</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Lead capture forms</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Home valuation calculator</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Neighborhood/market pages</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Google Maps integration</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">SSL security certificate</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">Local SEO optimization</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <CheckCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" />
            </div>
            <span class="text-black font-bold text-lg">30 days post-launch support</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decoration -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-green-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-black">How We Work Together</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-xl">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Free Consultation</h3>
            <p class="text-black font-medium">We discuss your market, ideal clients, and business goals. No sales pressure.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600 to-green-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-xl">
